{"entity": "RISC Architecture", "type": "architecture", "description": "RISC Architecture is a type of computer architecture based on Reduced Instruction Set Computing, listed as a topic within advanced processor architectures.<SEP>RISC Architecture là một mô hình máy tính với tập lệnh rút gọn, khác với CISC, nơi có tập lệnh phức tạp.<SEP>RISC Architecture is a computer architecture design characterized by a small set of simple, fixed-length instructions.<SEP>RISC Architecture refers to a type of computer processor architecture that uses a reduced instruction set."}
